OL,5,GIn the coming days many households will
OL,6,Ghear how their energy costs will rise.
OL,8,FMortgage rates are expected to rise
OL,9,Fnoticeably in the coming months.
OL,11,FAdd on the effects of inflation on
OL,12,Fday-to-day spending and some will
OL,13,Fsimply be watching the pennies or
OL,14,Ffinding ways to save money.
OL,16,FMeanwhile few will get a pay rise which
OL,17,Fcomes close to matching inflation.
OL,19,FFaced with economic uncertainty like
OL,20,Fthis, many will be weighing up their
OL,21,Fhousehold spending carefully.
OL,3,CUncertain times for broadcasters and
OL,4,Cstreaming services
