OL,5,FWill subscriptions to pay TV channels
OL,6,Fand streaming services suffer?
OL,8,FNaturally the question of value for
OL,9,Fmoney will vary from household to
OL,10,Fhousehold. But inevitably some pay for
OL,11,Fchannels they don't watch or services
OL,12,Fthey do not use routinely.
OL,14,FIt would also be interesting to know
OL,15,Fhow many people pay good money for pay
OL,16,FTV packages even when most of the
OL,17,Fchannels they watch are on Freeview and
OL,18,FFreesat.
OL,20,FFor some, cutting out Netflix or a pay
OL,21,FTV package could be an easy saving.
OL,3,CUncertain times for broadcasters and
OL,4,Cstreaming services
OL,22,                                   G2/5
