OL,5,FIt also reminds you what value for
OL,6,Fmoney the TV Licence is at barely #3 a
OL,7,Fweek and of the importance of the three
OL,8,Fmain commercial PSBs.
OL,10,FYes, the weekly cost of a TV Licence is
OL,11,Froughly the same as a decent coffee or
OL,12,Fa quality newspaper on a Saturday or
OL,13,FSunday. Its imperfections seem minor
OL,14,Fwhen the cost is expressed in these
OL,15,Fterms.
OL,17,FStill high inflation poses challenges
OL,18,Ffor the BBC  just like it does for
OL,19,Fanyone on a fixed income.
