OL,5,FMeanwhile the free-to-air commercial
OL,6,Fchannels will be anxious in case there
OL,7,Fis a downturn in advertising.
OL,9,FThis is a real risk. Anyone expressing
OL,10,Fa view on whether the PSBs should be
OL,11,Fallowed more advertising needs to
OL,12,Fconsider questions of sustainability.
OL,14,FOver the summer the Competition and
OL,15,FMarkets Authority held a consultation
OL,16,Fon whether to allow ITV to change the
OL,17,Fway advertising time is sold. The aim
OL,18,Fis to harmonise arrangements between
OL,19,Fthe former Granada and Carlton regions.
