OL,5,FThe CMA provisionally decided to allow
OL,6,Fthis and is likely to confirm this
OL,7,Fsoon.
OL,9,FMeanwhile the consultation by Ofcom on
OL,10,Fwhether to look at raising the
OL,11,Fpermitted amount of advertising ends
OL,12,Fnext week.
